  - Exports generate downloadable assets; frontend presents status and links.
- State Management
  - Use centralized API client with robust error handling; ensure null safety in responses.
- Data Consistency
  - Ensure event timestamps are normalized to UTC; handle time zone conversions on the frontend when displaying charts.
- Privacy & Compliance
  - Obfuscate PII in exports; respect opt-out preferences; provide an opt-out path in privacy settings.

